BuildFileDiff(String[], int) - Constructor for class net.ssehub.comani.analysis.variabilitychange.diff.BuildFileDiff
Construct a new BuildFileDiff.

This constructor will call the super constructor of FileDiff, which will start a line-wise analysis of the given diff lines calling the inherited methods BuildFileDiff.normalize(String, int) and BuildFileDiff.isVariabilityChange(String, int) defined in this class.
Counting the number of changed lines (regardless of variability information) is done in FileDiff.
